dcterms:creator: L. Hoyles
dcterms:description: The FLORINASH dataset includes clinical and biochemical data sets from a cohort of obese patients with hepatic steatosis, featuring sequencing data of the 16S rDNA gene from liver biopsies to study microbial composition and diversity.
dcterms:title: FLORINASH dataset
